link_title: How Jeff Bezos and Richard Branson’s Space Flights Will Differ | WSJ
description: Jeff Bezos, the founder of Blue Origin, and Richard Branson, the founder of Virgin Galactic, are in a head-to-head race to get into spaceThe billionaire founders of Blue Origin and Virgin Galactic will both be on board as the companies send their vessels to the edge of space. But their spacecraft, flight logistics and altitudes have some differences. link_title: Richard Branson Hopes To Beat Jeff Bezos Into Space This Sunday
description: Sir Richard Branson is set to lift off on a passenger test flight to the edge of space this Sunday, hoping to put the so-called “battle of the space billionaires” – Branson versus Amazon founder Jeff Bezos – to an end.
